This article is about the Legends timeline. You may be looking for the canon timeline, or the in-universe timeline of galactic history.

This article or section may contain original research or unverified claims.

Please help Wookieepedia by adding references.

This Star Wars Legends article contains information that is affected by the Star Wars: The Clone Wars project.

A definitive Legends Clone Wars timeline was never established by Lucasfilm. The exact chronology of the events described in this article is currently unknown.

This is a timeline for all Star Wars media considered canonical in the Legends continuity, including films, novels (both adult and young reader), eBooks, comics, short stories, television episodes, and video games.
